{"tid":1132264,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法案委員會仍未選出正副主席　謝偉俊：建制將有反制措施(監粗嚟)","createTime":"2019-04-30T07:39:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-30T07:50:43.000Z","uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9d3b4ec666add7182de47fb71b2143e7e345c83f","tid":1132264,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T07:39:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=346314\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D346314&d=jZUVzsr%2BlXwf2hbAbvJm1QHlXPv3B7QU%2BsV1%2BUkEKpk%3D&h=b95acbd2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D346314&h=288da1c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=346314</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】立法會修訂逃犯條例的法案委員會舉行第二次會議，仍然未能選出正副主席。盛傳會出任委員會主席的謝偉俊指泛民拖延選舉主席，建制派會有反制措施。<br />\n<br />\n謝偉俊︰「四小時選不到主席，從來未試過。在此情況下，為了立法會有效操作，不論為了今次，還是以今次作為先例，我們要考慮有沒有其他方案，在這個情況出現下，有沒有辦法由內會作恰當安排，令立法會可維持有效操作。」"},{"pid":"824bc780aeb0f22b0076a1386ea258c235d069e6","tid":1132264,"uid":4783,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T07:41:33.000Z","msg":"【最新】建制派聯署要求內會主席李慧琼發指引，要求由建制派最資深議員石禮謙出任逃犯條例法案委員會主席<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/?refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2F%3Frefer%3DShare&d=jZUVzsr%2BlXwf2hbAbvJm1QHlXPv3B7QU%2BsV1%2BUkEKpk%3D&h=4723b8e2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2F%3Frefer%3DShare&h=1b16d13d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/?refer=Share</a><br />\n<br />\n戇鳩到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係話要跟議事規則咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2e0b06f7ce05828fca884a6d9b784a320552191","tid":1132264,"uid":14478,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"824bc780aeb0f2